@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bxrtto(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v1 + 0.71) - wp.exp(v0 + 0.98)) * tmp)
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.exp(v2))
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.91)))
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.62) * 0.05) + ((v2 + 0.19 / v0 + 0.38) + (v2 + 0.19 + v0 + 0.72)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(v1) * wp.cos((v1 + 0.26 + v1 + 0.71)))
    data[tid] = v0
